{{ 'section-kaahu-content-page.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{%- case page.handle -%}
  {%- when 'care', 'care-instructions' -%}
    <main class="kaahu-content-page kcp-content">
      <header class="kcp-hero">
        <div class="kcp-wrap">
          <p class="kcp-eyebrow">Care</p>
          <hr class="kcp-rule" aria-hidden="true">
          <h1>A few quiet ways to keep it well.</h1>
          <div class="kcp-hero__lede kcp-rich"><p>Each Kaahu bag is made from natural fibers and built by hand. These notes help it last - gracefully and naturally, just as it was made.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="kcp-wrap kcp-hero__image">
          <div class="kcp-frame kcp-frame--wide">
            <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0709/9046/3195/files/DSC00133.jpg?v=1775156033" alt="Close-up of a Kaahu bag's fabric and finish" width="1800" height="900" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high">
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="kcp-notes">
        <div class="kcp-wrap">
          <div class="kcp-rows">
            <div class="kcp-row"><div class="kcp-row__label">Spot clean</div><div class="kcp-row__text kcp-rich"><p>For small marks or spills, use a damp cloth and gentle pressure. Avoid soaps, detergents, or solvents - natural fibers respond best to a lighter touch.</p></div></div>
            <div class="kcp-row"><div class="kcp-row__label">Air dry</div><div class="kcp-row__text kcp-rich"><p>Let your bag dry in a shaded, well-ventilated space. Keep it away from direct sunlight or artificial heat, which can shrink or fade the fibers over time.</p></div></div>
            <div class="kcp-row"><div class="kcp-row__label">Store thoughtfully</div><div class="kcp-row__text kcp-rich"><p>When it's resting, keep your bag in a cool, dry place. The cotton dust bag it arrives in guards against moisture and dust, while letting the materials breathe.</p></div></div>
            <div class="kcp-row"><div class="kcp-row__label">Natural fibers, natural rhythm</div><div class="kcp-row__text kcp-rich"><p>Jute and organic cotton breathe, shift, and age with time. Keep them dry and away from prolonged humidity to preserve their texture and strength.</p></div></div>
            <div class="kcp-row"><div class="kcp-row__label">Mend what matters</div><div class="kcp-row__text kcp-rich"><p>If your bag ever needs attention, repair before you replace. A small mend carries it further - and adds to the story it holds.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="kcp-close kcp-wrap">
        <div class="kcp-rich"><p>For anything else, write to <a href="mailto:care@kaahu.us">care@kaahu.us</a>. We're here.</p></div>
        <p class="kcp-sign">Used gently, a good bag only gets better.</p>
      </section>
    </main>

  {%- when 'faq' -%}
    <main class="kaahu-content-page kcp-content">
      <header class="kcp-hero kcp-wrap kcp-faq-wrap">
        <p class="kcp-eyebrow">FAQ</p>
        <hr class="kcp-rule" aria-hidden="true">
        <h1>Questions, answered.</h1>
        <div class="kcp-hero__lede kcp-rich"><p>For anything not covered here, write to us at <a href="mailto:care@kaahu.us">care@kaahu.us</a> - we respond within one business day.</p></div>
      </header>

      <nav class="kcp-jump kcp-wrap kcp-faq-wrap" aria-label="FAQ categories">
        <a href="#orders">Orders &amp; shipping</a>
        <a href="#materials">Product &amp; materials</a>
        <a href="#gifting">Gifting</a>
        <a href="#support">Support</a>
        <a href="#social">News &amp; social</a>
        <a href="#pricing">Pricing &amp; refunds</a>
        <a href="#payment">Payment</a>
